extendedInfo.description: The wallpapers that will make you delicately say:  'Oh look at this! It is so cute!'  Everything that you call sweet and lovable is collected in these wallpapers. Each of them will bring a smile on your face and make you feel happy! The cute backgrounds will easily creep under your skin! Keep changing them and they will undoubtedly make your day! - Easy-to-browse interface enables you to find the desired background in no time!- Customize the wallpaper to fit your taste and screen!- Zoom, un-zoom, rotate, move, scale, adjust brightness, add various effects and save your background designYou know it when you see it, but in a fashion similar to defining humor it is somewhat elusive. To have cuteness is to be subscribed to some vague aesthetic criteria which has no specific rules or boundaries. Babies can be endlessly adorable. The emotional feeling one can feel when exposed to cuteness can vary. Sweet is the kind of thing we tend to accept as universal. The phrase Thatâs cute, seem to be speaking to something we can all understand. Cuteness can come in any colour, but the baby colours of pink or blue or maybe yellow seem to be preferred. Puppies and kittens are already irresistible! But cute colours alone are often employed for graphics, to give it that childish innocence that, uh, girls in particular, love. Oh, and then thereâs white. Remember black? Remember when we wanted all our technology to be black? Not sweet. These days itâs white. Or pink, or â¦Did we miss fur? Why are tribbles adorable, even without eyes, because theyâre covered in fur. Fur is the great cutifier of all things (and we laugh at plushie fetishists).Are eggs sweet? Not sure. However, cover it in fur, add a couple of eyes and â¦ hey, youâre not having that for breakfastâhow cruel are you?Smallness is also a required ingredient. Even when a cute image is rendered large, itâs important to understand its representation as something of a smaller size. Giant mice resemble rats, and are not lovely at all. The dire warning to all potential puppy-buyers is often 'Remember, they turn into dogs.'All the lovely tiny and adorable things are collected at one place. By downloading these wallpapers you will get a long list of them. Find your favorite one (if possible only one) and make people say : 'How cute  your wallpapers are!' Cheer up your phone with endless sweetness!
